title: ValueTaskBuilder.Combine
content:
ValueTaskBuilder.Combine 
Combine 

 Chains together a step with its following step.
 Note that this requires that the first step has no result.
 This prevents constructs like `task { return 1; return 2; }`.

title: ValueTaskBuilder.TryFinally
content:
ValueTaskBuilder.TryFinally 
TryFinally 

 Wraps a step in a try/finally. This catches exceptions both in the evaluation of the function
 to retrieve the step, and in the continuation of the step (if any).

title: ValueTaskBuilder.TryWith
content:
ValueTaskBuilder.TryWith 
TryWith 

 Wraps a step in a try/with. This catches exceptions both in the evaluation of the function
 to retrieve the step, and in the continuation of the step (if any).

title: ValueTaskBuilder.While
content:
ValueTaskBuilder.While 
While

title: Effect.recover
content: Effect.recover recover Recovers a failed effect by producing an in case of failure. If the effect was already successful, f is never run.

title: Effect.tryRecover
content: Effect.tryRecover tryRecover Potentially recovers a failed effect by producing an Result{'a, 'e} in case of failure. If the effect was already successful, f is never run.

title: Effect.onError
content: Effect.onError onError Potentially recovers a failed effect by producing a new effect in case of failure. If the effect was already successful, f is never run.

changeError

zip
